{"tid":1444822,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論］係時候決定下次大型和理非遊行日期","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:31:06.000Z","uid":135398,"like":37,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9ab8e8eac2210a563ba1be3709591f83dae6e2c3","tid":1444822,"uid":135398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"呢排每個星期最少都同時搞兩個，大量分薄咗我地嘅人力物力，好多時候行完遊行就直接開波，令到勇武同和理非差距愈拉愈大。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且大家都留意到我地每次出黎嘅人數都愈黎愈小，同一時間手足又比警犬愈拉愈多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係時候比個星期大家休息同準備下一次大型遊行！跟返勝利方程式，和理非-勇武-死線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />824<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />831"},{"pid":"075e480e0157c4a6f21c42996e0f9d25eb463959","tid":1444822,"uid":67041,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:21:21.000Z","msg":"建議9 月，等條7 婆知道唔係開左學就無人出"},{"pid":"be7739163ec0363658bce9241e3a9b58ae9723f4","tid":1444822,"uid":203402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"推佢老母"},{"pid":"d1e5dd44b63bab941fd95f55d95a88c9dafe128b","tid":1444822,"uid":203402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:22:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c096fe3170f3909833e607d961db76a7be06f8f2","tid":1444822,"uid":203402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bac1f02977bd1bed6e73ccc4e6b218479073c02b","tid":1444822,"uid":203402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:23:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45059b1e76ac5df1aaa63b1c67c97f0e9e67e9f1","tid":1444822,"uid":203402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,